{"tid":3702,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG既成立令我諗起腎仔一隻歌","createTime":"2016-11-26T08:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T08:55:05.000Z","uid":5990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8dca66556b3c87c27d0fbf6a845d55fc6024b5b6","tid":3702,"uid":5990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"《今生不回家》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/jqzQq28QUAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjqzQq28QUAc&d=APckT7yvosIwZc4AGUGEJcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f0e47fe8\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/jqzQq28QUAc</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當一個新移民 切斷上半生 找一個新祖國繼續做人<br />\n回望每一組歸家腳印 沒想到 護照要蓋滿新的印<br />\n曾以為有家就是安穩 當天氣改變世道人心<br />\n再溫馨都感覺似被幽禁 至發現城牆外面曠野那天空不算暗</span><br />\n<br />\n多謝高登陪伴我一直以黎既成長 我現時所得大多數的知識和價值觀其實都來自高登。今次的離開 多少都會唔捨得 感覺好似斷左根咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奈何林早洩一而再再而三咁踩高登仔底線 又專制又亂bam人又毫無長進毫無作為 高登仔迫不得已先另覓他鄉 「找一個新祖國繼續做人」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但無論如何，LIHKG已成立 以前熟悉的名字都逐漸見得返 一個討論區重要的不過是人 而我地仍然可以在新土地繼續生活落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實香港面對的情況咪又係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係 身為香港人既我地 未來又能否找一個新祖國重聚？"},{"pid":"445534b755bd89bf2b1def13237cd72e0edbb213","tid":3702,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}